Authors: Yiyan Zheng, Yi Ping Zhang, Lisa B. E. Shields, Yongjie Zhang, Marcus W. Siu, Darlene A. Burke, Jianhong Zhu, Xiaoling Hu, John R. Dimar, Christopher B. Shields
Title: Effect of Heparin Following Cervical Spinal Cord Injuries in Rats
Abstract: BACKGROUND: Risks of neurological deterioration after heparin administration following cervical spinal cord injury (SCI) in humans are unknown.
